title: BEST Basketball Player 🏀⛹️ Talking Tom Shorts (S3 Episode 7)
description:
Basketball’s a great game, but it’s not really fair, is it? 🏀 It’s hard to slam dunk the ball when you’re small, as Talking Ginger knows only too well. 🤾

While Talking Tom, Talking Angela, Talking Hank, and Talking Becca can all fly through the air and effortlessly drop the ball through the hoop, 💨😎 poor Ginger can’t reach. And every time Ginger finds a way to get bigger air, Talking Ben says it’s against the rules.🚫

Is there a way to make the game fun for everyone, including Ginger? There’s a courtside seat reserved just for you, 🏟️ so hit play and let’s find out! ▶️

title: Yard Sale 💰🏠 Talking Tom Shorts
description:
A yard sale can be a great way to clear out some old stuff and make a bit of cash while you're at it. 💵 Or, if you’re a customer, they’re a great place to pick up a bargain. 🤑 But a good yard sale is based on trust and respect - two ideas Roy the Rakoon knows nothing about! 🦝😠

This time the rascally robber is using his powers of disguise to trick the friends into giving their stuff away for nothing. 😮 But they’re onto his scheme, and are about to turn the tables… 🤔😉

Hit play to find out how the friends catch the crook and get their stuff back! ▶️🕵️‍♀️

title: Tricky Traps for Roy - Talking Tom Shorts
description:
Does your home have a security system? 🛡️ A burglar alarm? 🚨 Some sensor-activated lights, maybe? 💡

How about a handful of MARBLES on the floor? Or a BUCKET of water on a tripwire? A cake CATAPULT!? 🎂💥

Talking Tom’s anti-burglary set-up looks more like a collection of pranks than a watertight home protection system. 😂 And that means you can be sure that something’s going to go wrong… 🫣 and just as sure that it’ll be really, really funny when it does! 🤣

Tune in to find out who gets a bucket of water on his head, 🪣 and who gets a face full of cake. 🤬 Roy the Rakoon is in the neighbourhood, so maybe it’ll be him. 🦝 But maybe not… 😁

title: Elevator Escape 🏙️🛗 Talking Tom Shorts: Epic Runs
description:
Have you ever been to the top of a really high building? 🏙️ Did you take the elevator or the stairs? 🛗 You took the stairs!? How many steps was it!? 🥵

When Talking Tom takes a safe full of gold to the top of an under-construction skyscraper, he thinks it’ll be out of reach from those light-fingered Rakoonz. 🦝 But he couldn’t be more wrong! 🫣

Roy Rakoon and his sidekick snatch the safe, and so begins the most… vertical chase of Tom’s life. 🏃💨 Can he reach the ground fast enough using the stairs? Or is there maybe a quicker way to catch those robbers? 🤔

title: Smile for the Camera! 📸😁 Talking Tom & Friends | Animated Cartoons
description:
Things look big in photos when they’re close to the camera, right? 📷 And small when they’re far away… 🔭 don’t they? It’s just a trick of perspective. Or, is it? 🧐

Imagine you’re posing for a photo with a taller friend, 👨‍👧 and you take a step towards the camera so that you’ll look the same height in the photo. But after the photo’s taken, you’re actually taller FOR REAL! 😮 That’s EXACTLY what happens to the Pets! 🤯

Poor Gus ends up so tiny that he’s in danger of being squashed by a giant Squeak. 🐜🦶 Fortunately, Sugar knows how to keep things in perspective, 🦄 and with a few clever camera tricks, everything gets back to normal. Well, almost normal…🤣

description:

Talking Tom and his friends get around using pretty much every kind of transport you can think of. Cars, bikes, boats, ships, planes… even a jetpack! 🚀 WHOAH! 🫣

And you know what they say… life’s not about the destination, it’s about the journey. 🛣️ And that’s certainly true of all these transport-tastic Talking Tom episodes. So just sit back, and enjoy the ride! 😊

#talkingtom #livestream #cartoon 

Hi, guys! I’m Talking Tom – welcome to my channel. It’s so cool to meet you!

☆ SUBSCRIBE
Subscribe to my channel so you don’t miss a minute of the fun – there’s going to be A LOT of it! 😆 Just follow the link 👉 https://www.youtube.com/user/TalkingTomCat

Stay awesome! 👌😎
Tom

title: Ice-Cream Chase 🍦🚨 Talking Tom Shorts: Epic Runs
description:
Do you love ice cream? 🍨 Silly question… who doesn’t?! 😋

Nothing beats an ice cream on a hot day at the beach, 🏖️ which is why Talking Tom and his friends have their very own ICE CREAM MACHINE. That’s right. Ice cream… on tap! 🍦🚰

You’re jealous, of course, but not so jealous you’d actually STEAL the ice cream machine. But that’s exactly what Roy Rakoon is up to. 🦝😲 Can Tom catch him and return the ice cream machine before all the ice cream melts away?🫢

Only one way to find out! Get yourself a treat from the freezer, 🍧 and hit play! ▶️

title: 🧁 The Cupcake Dream & More 🍭😴 Talking Tom Shorts (S2 Episode 55)
description:
Have you ever been woken up from an AMAZING dream? 😴💭 All you want to do is get back to sleep, right? But it’s never that easy… 😒

The exact same thing happened to Talking Hank when he dreamed of a GIANT cupcake. 🧁 Just as he was about to take his first bite too! 😋

Despite napping pretty much all day every day, Hank still seems to find himself at the center of the action when things get crazy at the Talking Tom & Friends house. 🏡 As you’ll see from this HILARIOUS compilation, sometimes he brings it on himself, and sometimes he’s just at the wrong place (usually on the toilet 🚽) at the wrong time!

So, just like Hank would do, grab some snacks, 🍿 stretch out on the couch, 🛋️ and hit play! ▶️

description:

It’s time to reveal the “best of” collection for Season 2 of Talking Tom Shorts! 🎬🥳

Which episodes made it into the Top 5?! 🤔 You’re about to find out! They’re full of fun, adventure, and non-stop laughs – and they’re some of our all-time favorites too! ❤️

There’s the episode where the girls totally wrecked the toilet! ​​🚽😬 Can you believe it?! Oh and the one where the guys basically tried to destroy the house! 🤣🏡 There are mysteries like Talking Hank’s disappearing birthday cake, invasions from bugs, and… ALIENS! 🛸 Yeah, you read that right. Aliens! 🤯

Grab some snacks and get comfy. 🍿 This is gonna be a super fun ride through some of the best episodes of Talking Tom Shorts Season 2. 🏆 Watch this video now for the non-stop version, or use the links below and jump in and out as you please! 👇

00:00 💥 We Destroyed the Toilet (Season 2, Episode 26): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhTo6IVYJCU

title: Best. Summer. EVER! ☀️💦 Talking Tom Shorts Cartoon
description:
It’s HOT outside! ☀️What should Talking Tom and all his friends do? 🤔

😎 They’ve got lots of ideas for awesome summer adventures – a few of which OBVIOUSLY involve water balloon battles! 🎈💦 It’s the best way to cool off and have fun, right?! 🙌 Who do you think has the best balloon skills? You’ll have to watch to find out… 😜

But that’s not all! 🎉 This cartoon collection is packed with fun, including a trip to the desert, a beach day that one of the friends can’t HELP but turn crazy, and a swimming pool misadventure involving Talking Ben’s new shrink ray invention! 😃

It’s all happening in this five-episode Talking Tom Shorts collection. 🎬🍿 Ready to join in on all the summertime awesomeness? ☀️ Watch now by hitting ▶️ or by using the links below! 👇

🎮🤩 Talking Tom and his pets LOVE playing mini-games like Space Trails! ☄️ Play with them now in My Talking Tom 2! https://outfit7.com/apps/download/mtt2-yt-description

3… 2… 1! BLAST OFF! 🚀🌠 Tom’s pets are in space to race their super amazing rockets. 🛸 But there’s only one left… And both Tom AND Squeak want to join in on the fun! 😮😜 Who’s going to get to join the interstellar race?

And will they even be able to pilot the powerful rocket? 😬 It’s not as easy as it looks! 🤦 And it turns out there are LOTS of things you can crash into if you’re not quick enough to dodge them! 🌌🤣

💫 See if you can dodge the obstacles and make the longest trail in the Space Trails mini-game! 🎮 My Talking Tom 2 is available to download and play now on Android and iOS: https://outfit7.com/apps/download/mtt2-yt-description
